  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个需求流转的状态图，核心是从创建到最终决策的完整流程。起点应该是新建状态，我管它叫\"in preparation\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "ip"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点指向in preparation。那接下来需求会去哪里？是直接到评审，还是先经过产品负责人？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ip",
        "po"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "产品负责人这边有两条路径进来：一个是全新的需求从in preparation过来，另一个是已经定义好义务但被打回的需求，我称之为\"in preparation with Obligations defined\"。这两条都汇聚到专家评估环节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ip",
        "inPObl",
        "iex",
        "po"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在产品负责人这个子区域里画了从ip到iex，以及从inPObl到iex的流转。专家评估之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ip",
        "iex",
        "inPObl"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "专家评估完进入QG Review，这是质量门禁。然后到发布管理团队做最终决策，有四种可能结果：直接通过、不做、需要补充义务定义、或者上升到管理决策。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "iex",
        "qgr",
        "rm",
        "p",
        "wd",
        "obg",
        "md"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：QG Review之后分出四条分支——passed、Won't do、Obligations defined、Management Decision。其中Obligations defined会回到之前你说的那个带义务的准备状态，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "qgr",
        "obg",
        "inPObl"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是那个闭环。不过我想把整个流程包装成一个大区域，叫\"The Other Path\"，里面再分三个子区域：Product Owner、Expert、Release Management，这样层级更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "pod",
        "po",
        "ex",
        "rm"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "结构搭好了，三个子区域都按从左到右的方向排布。不过我注意到Obligations defined到in preparation with Obligations的箭头你还没明确说，是要隐含处理还是显式画出？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "obg",
        "inPObl"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这个不用画箭头，inPObl是独立状态，从起点逻辑上理解成循环回去就行。对了，Obligations defined旁边我习惯标注\"back to PO\"，提醒这是返回产品负责人的路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "obg",
        "back to po"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "刚才我把Release Management拼写错了，写成了\"Mangement\"，现在修正为\"Release Management\"。另外确认一下QG Review的四种结果箭头都从它出发，没错吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "rm",
        "qgr",
        "wd",
        "p",
        "obg",
        "md"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，四种决策方向都从QG Review出来。整体方向保持从左到右，起点在最左，各子区域内部也保持LR方向。看起来结构完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "direction LR",
        "pod",
        "po",
        "ex",
        "rm"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "最终确认：起点→in preparation，进入Product Owner区域后可流向专家评估，经QG Review后在Release Management处四向决策，Obligations defined形成闭环返回。整个流程封装在The Other Path内，层级和流向都符合你的要求。",
